{t:I Will Extol You My God (F) #51}
{st:}

SONG 51
CHORD F

I will extol You my God and my King,  
I will bless Your name forever and ever.  
Everyday will I bless You O Lord,   
I will glorify Your name forevermore.  
For You are great and greatly to be praised,  
We shall declare Your mighty acts,  
We will tell of Your goodness and kindness to us,  
Our mouths shall speak the praise of our God.   




